text:
Ayesha Takia: Plastic surgery gone wrong Ayesha Takia: Plastic surgery gone wrong Source : 
Bollywood and cosmetic surgeries go hand in hand. Most celebs go to any lengths to enhance their looks and the end results are sometimes strong evidences. Such is the case with Ayesha Takia. 
Once considered to be the cutest actress of the cinema industry looks unrecognizable now.
